aplo-r:temporalExtent.Learner%20Connie.Metadata.Knowledge%20Graph%20Documentation%20Planning.Knowledge%20Graph%20Documentation%20Planning%20Practice%20Update.2026-03-07T14%3A03%3A00Z%20to%202026-03-07T14%3A28%3A00Z a aplo-ont:TemporalExtent ;
